subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which famous battle took place in 1891 at Amber?
question_hi: 1891 में अमर पर किस संघी का महत्ता हुआ ?
explanation_en: The Battle of Amber took place in 1891 between the Rajput king of Amber, Maharaja Man Singh I, and the British East India Company.
